body:
The following query uses the [$search](pipe.$search) stage to perform
the following actions:

- Search for movies that have the term `summer` in the title.

- Sort the results by score in descending order and for results
  with identical scores, sort arbitrarily.

The query uses the [$limit](manual/reference/operator/aggregation/limit) stage to limit the output to `5`
documents. It also uses the [$project](manual/reference/operator/aggregation/project) stage to perform the
following actions:

- Omit all fields except `_id` and `title` in the results.

- Add a field named `score`.

**Input:**

```json
db.movies.aggregate([
  {
    "$search": {
      "text": {
        "path": "title",
        "query": "summer"
      },
      "sort": {score: {$meta: "searchScore"}}
    }
  },
  {
    "$limit": 5
  },
  {
    "$project": {
      "_id": 1,
      "title": 1,
      "score": {$meta: "searchScore"}
    }
  }
])
```

**Output:**

```json
[
  {
    _id: ObjectId("573a1398f29313caabcea21e"),
    title: 'Summer',
    score: 3.5844719409942627
  },
  {
    _id: ObjectId("573a13a6f29313caabd18eca"),
    title: 'Summer Things',
    score: 3.000213623046875
  },
  {
    _id: ObjectId("573a13b8f29313caabd4c1d0"),
    title: 'Summer Palace',
    score: 3.000213623046875
  },
  {
    _id: ObjectId("573a1394f29313caabcde8e8"),
    title: 'Summer Stock',
    score: 3.000213623046875
  },
  {
    _id: ObjectId("573a13acf29313caabd284fa"),
    title: 'Wolf Summer',
    score: 3.000213623046875
  }
]
```

